          <title>Roosevelt Hotel to shut down as migrant arrival center: NYC Mayor Adams</title>
          <description><![CDATA[MANHATTAN, N.Y. (PIX11) – The migrant arrival center at the Roosevelt Hotel in Manhattan is set to shut down, New York City Mayor Eric Adams will announce on Monday. More than 173,000 migrants have gone through the site since it opened in May 2023, according to city data.]]></description>
